<span id="freeTextContainer2744832536648745161">4.5/5 stars. If you&apos;ve suffered from depression and/or anxiety yourself at some point in your life or you know someone that has (and it&apos;s very likely that you do) this book is an absolute must-read. </span>
  <span id="freeText2744832536648745161" style="display:none">4.5/5 stars. If you've suffered from depression and/or anxiety yourself at some point in your life or you know someone that has (and it's very likely that you do) this book is an absolute must-read. </span>
